OL,3,CNew school guidance issued for PE
OL,4,Clessons during Ramadan
OL,6,FSport is thirsty work on a normal day,
OL,7,Fmaking a PE lesson that bit harder for
OL,8,FMuslim students fasting during Ramadan.
OL,10,FOvernight on Monday March 11, many
OL,11,FMuslims across the country began
OL,12,Ffasting for the Holy Month.
OL,14,FFor those who are old enough, and
OL,15,Fchoosing to take part in Fasting, it
OL,16,Fmeans they won't be able to eat or
OL,17,Fdrink during much of the day - for the
OL,18,Fnext 30 days or so.
