OL,3,CNew school guidance issued for PE
OL,4,Clessons during Ramadan
OL,6,FFor school pupils taking part in sport
OL,7,Fand PE lessons during the month, not
OL,8,Fbeing able to drink water can prove
OL,9,Fchallenging.
OL,11,FStudents at Stuart Bathurst Catholic
OL,12,FHigh School in Wednesbury told ITV
OL,13,FNews: "Anything can happen, you don't
OL,14,Fknow, your body isn't hydrated or
OL,15,Fdoesn't have enough food in it, so you
OL,16,Fcan pass out or have a serious
OL,17,Fcondition."
OL,19,FAnother said: "We used to do track for
OL,20,FPE and one time I wasn't allowed water
OL,21,Fand my head started aching."
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G2/11
