OL,6,FWhile another noted: "I've been
OL,7,Ffasting for quite a few years, but
OL,8,Fsometimes it does get difficult."
OL,10,F'I didn't want to be treated any
OL,11,Fdifferently' says Dr Irfan Khawaja,
OL,12,Fthe man behind the guidance
OL,14,FBut, groundbreaking new guidance for
OL,15,Fschools on how to manage and adapt
OL,16,Flessons for fasting students is hoping
OL,17,Fto change those concerns.
