OL,3,CNew school guidance issued for PE
OL,4,Clessons during Ramadan
OL,6,FThe new guidance offers advice to
OL,7,Fteachers on how they can adapt
OL,8,Fclasses, with easy tweaks like keeping
OL,9,Fthem indoors instead of outdoors
OL,10,Fduring the summer, allowing students
OL,11,Fto coach from the sidelines and
OL,12,Flowering the intensity of lessons for
OL,13,Fpupils.
