OL,6,FDr Irfan Khawaja, a senior lecturer at
OL,7,FBirmingham City University, and the
OL,8,Fman who wrote the guidance, said it's
OL,9,Fbecause of his own experiences at
OL,10,Fschool: "At the age of 16 I was a
OL,11,Ffasting PE student doing GCSE PE and I
OL,12,Fdid the multi-stage fitness test, or
OL,13,Fsome know it as the bleep test.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G5/11
