OL,6,FHe continued: "Now, I was nil-by-
OL,7,Fmouth, which includes no water, now
OL,8,Frunning a VO2 max test when you are
OL,9,Ffasting naturally has some serious
OL,10,Frisks associated with it, but being
OL,11,Fthe young 16 year old that I was, I
OL,12,Ffully engaged in it, I didn't want to
OL,13,Fraise awareness to the fact that I was
OL,14,Ffasting, cause I didn't want to be
OL,15,Ftreated any differently, I just wanted
OL,16,Fto carry on with my friends."
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G6/11
