OL,3,CNew school guidance issued for PE
OL,4,Clessons during Ramadan
OL,6,F'There's no teaching in the religion
OL,7,Fthat says when you're fasting you
OL,8,Fcan't engage in physical activity,'
OL,9,Fsays Shaykh Ibrahim Mogra, from the
OL,10,FMuslim Council of Britain
OL,12,FWith this year's fasts due to start at
OL,13,Faround 4.30am, and end at 6-7pm each
OL,14,Fday, many Imams across the country
OL,15,Fhave welcomed Dr Khawaja's guidance.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G7/11
