OL,3,CNew school guidance issued for PE
OL,4,Clessons during Ramadan
OL,6,FThe guidance has been published and
OL,7,Fendorsed by the Association for
OL,8,FPhysical Education, and endorsed by
OL,9,Fthe Muslim Council of Britain, The
OL,10,FYouth Sport Trust and the Chartered
OL,11,FInstitute for the Management of Sport
OL,12,Fand Physical Activity.
OL,14,FShaykh Ibrahim Mogra, from the Muslim
OL,15,FCouncil of Britain, said it'll help
OL,16,Fstop students from ducking out of
OL,17,Fsports lessons: "So, in the past it
OL,18,Fwas not uncommon to hear stories of
OL,19,FMuslim students refusing to
OL,20,Fparticipate in physical activity
OL,21,Fbecause they said 'We're fasting.'
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G8/11
