OL,3,CNew school guidance issued for PE
OL,4,Clessons during Ramadan
OL,6,FHe added: "But there's no teaching in
OL,7,Fthe religion that says when you're
OL,8,Ffasting you can't engage in physical
OL,9,Factivity.
OL,11,F"Some of the tweaks a PE teacher can
OL,12,Fmake, for example, in a swimming
OL,13,Flesson, is because water should not
OL,14,Fenter the mouth and thereby the
OL,15,Fthroat, which would nullify the fast,
OL,16,Fis to ensure that they do activities
OL,17,Fwithin the water which will minimise
OL,18,Fthe possibility of that, so to do
OL,19,Fbackstrokes or treading in the water."
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G9/11
