OL,3,CNew school guidance issued for PE
OL,4,Clessons during Ramadan
OL,6,F'Young people today will definitely
OL,7,Fbenefit from this guidance,' says
OL,8,FBoxing coach Haseebah Abdullah
OL,10,FOne England Boxing Coach who was a
OL,11,FCommonwealth Games Home Town Hero says
OL,12,Fthe guidance only helps to break down
OL,13,Fbarriers.
OL,15,FHaseebah Abdullah said: "I wish there
OL,16,Fwas someone out there that could
OL,17,Frepresent us and help us out during
OL,18,Fthis month because as young people,
OL,19,Fwhen we're heard, we feel included, we
OL,20,Ffeel like we're actually being valued.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G10/11
