OL,6,FShe concluded: "I think that's really
OL,7,Freally important and young people
OL,8,Ftoday will definitely benefit from
OL,9,Fthis guidance."
OL,11,FAround 75% of schools have taken up
OL,12,Fthe guidance, but it's hoped that will
OL,13,Fsoon become 100% so all Muslim pupils
OL,14,Fcan keep active during Ramadan.
